data.chText: 这是个极其重要的问题。
data.enText: This is a matter of the utmost importance.

data.chText: 你们对这个文件的研究应该慎之又慎。
data.enText: You should study this document with the utmost care.

data.chText: 最大量；最大限度；极限；最大可能

data.enText: Our resources are strained to the utmost.

data.chText: 他使尽浑身解数劝我别去。
data.enText: He did his utmost (= tried as hard as possible) to persuade me not to go.

tr: (comparatives of `far') most remote in space or time or order
example: had traveled to the farthest frontier
don't go beyond the farthermost (or furthermost) tree
explored the furthest reaches of space
the utmost tip of the peninsula
to the last measure of human endurance
whether they were accomplices in the last degree or a lesser one was...to be determined individually

value.def: You can use utmost to emphasize the importance or seriousness of something or to emphasize the way that it is done.

example.ex: It is a matter of the utmost urgency to find out what has happened to these people...
example.tran: 当务之急是要弄清楚这些人出了什么事。

example.ex: Security matters are treated with the utmost seriousness...
example.tran: 安全问题的处理极其严肃。

example.ex: You should proceed with the utmost caution...
Utmost care must be taken not to spill any of the contents.
example.tran: 千万注意里面的东西一点都不能洒出来。

value.def: If you say that you are doing your utmost to do something, you are emphasizing that you are trying as hard as you can to do it.

example.ex: He would have done his utmost to help her, of that she was certain...
example.tran: 他肯定会尽最大努力帮她，这一点她非常肯定。

example.ex: He will try his utmost to help them by means of his conventional medical knowledge.
example.tran: 他将会用自己的传统医学知识尽全力帮助他们。

value.def: If you say that something is done to the utmost, you are emphasizing that it is done to the greatest extent, amount, or degree possible.

example.ex: My limited diplomatic skills were tested to the utmost...
example.tran: 我有限的外交手腕儿受到了极其严峻的考验。

example.ex: The best plan is to continue to attack him to the utmost of our power.
example.tran: 最佳方案就是继续不遗余力地攻击他。

trans: 特别善意性，最大善意性；最大诚信，绝对诚信，最好信念
